data.description: Welcome home! This charming single-story home is the perfect place to start a family or enjoy peaceful retirement living. Featuring three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and two large living areas, this home has plenty of space for your family to spread out and relax. You will love to entertain in the spacious kitchen featuring a bar area for extra seating or food prep space. Refrigerated air ensures everyone stays cool and comfortable year-round. Whether you are entertaining friends or just spending time with your loved ones, this home provides the perfect backdrop for making cherished memories. Plus, you'll find plenty of room outside for hosting friends or family gatherings in the backyard. With plenty of space for family fun and relaxation, this is the perfect place to call home.
